<br>
Your wisdom is 214,<br>
<br>
Get rid of the BCP - it sucks bad, and get a shroud of nature (6wis 8fr/cr) = you can most likely solo this spawn if your careful, it gives you wisdom in a place you lack it, and free's up some other slots which you can make better use of.<br>
<br>
Get a Tranix crown (20MR 13ac +15chr eff serpent sight), or a Froglok Crown (20CR/FR 12ac) = 216wis<br>
(better resists and ac) again you can group in Lguk to get a frog crown - a tranix crown will be harder to come by<br>
<br>
Try to replace both rings with velium fire opal rings (6ac +65hp) or diamond rings (+8all resists), 202wisdom<br>
<br>
Gloves, eventually i'd try and upgrade to coldain skin gloves (6wis/int 9sta 20hp/mana 12ac)<br>
<br>
Jasper gold earrings - i'd recommend replacing these with either an earring of essence (10mr +30hp) for raid situations, or electrum black sapphire earrings (2ac 35hp, 25mana) again, the earring of essence is quite an easy camp, you could possibly do it solo, if not 2 of you would easily manage it and its not that rare..<br>
Or Forest Hoops - 2ac 3wis/sta/dex of course...<br>
<br>
range slot - medicine totem - 5ac 5wis probably sells for 5k ?<br>
<br>
secondary hand - book of obulus is good - 8wis/int +45mana 5FR/CR - again some resists for raids drops in KC basement off spectral turnkeys (probably 1in3 drop rate) i'm not sure if the basement is a little too high or not tho, or if you can get a group camping the exit area of Chardok you might be able to get a sarnak battleshield (25ac 40hp 5sta/str 10MR/CR/FR) rare drops but a few days there and you should see a couple drop ?<br>
<br>
arms - hunt in KC and get some ES arms - they drop off drovlarg sentries.<br>
<br>
Primary Hand - Paw of Opolla maybe ?<br>
<br>
Just some advice anyhow :)<br>
<br>
Peoni Greenleaf &lt;Defiant&gt;<br>
Naturewalker of Tunare<br>
Vallon Zek <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showMessage?topicID=3277.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showMessage?topicID=3242.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.emailToFriend?topicID=3278.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.threadControl?topicID=3278.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3278.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3278.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral">General - EQ<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm27">General - DAOC<option value="thedruidsgrovegeneralot">General - OT<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm18">FAQ & Index<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm20">Spoilers<option value="thedruidsgrovespells">Spells<option value="thedruidsgrovequests">Quests<option value="thedruidsgrovedruidicequipment">Druidic Equipment<option value="thedruidsgrovehuntingguide">Hunting